Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.95,0:01:11.29,落第骑士,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs29\be20}字幕  時雨初空字幕組        手抄&時軸  西行寺幽幽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.12,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k383}目標遙指最高處  A brave new word
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:18.98,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k386}以那熱情的劍鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:25.74,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k676}刻印在這片舞台的是  It's my soul(Yeah)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:30.49,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k393}不容任何人觸碰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.49,0:01:34.47,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k398}你我共鳴的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:40.55,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k608}命運想必正是在此刻決定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:45.56,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k342}儘管嘲笑我的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:49.50,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k394}儘管去驕傲自滿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.92,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k342}迷茫踏在腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.91,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k299}Let's go ahead!～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:02:00.58,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k380}所以正是現在將其破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:04.48,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k390}是啊 把那堵塞我明天的沉重大門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:09.18,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k470}盡全力使出渾身解數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:12.26,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k308}以經歷千錘百煉的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:16.00,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k374}凝聚一擊 將其突破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.92,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k392}是啊 把那阻擋我未來的厚重大門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.92,0:02:24.83,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k491}起死回生的瞬間已經到來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:26.77,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k194}絕境之高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:31.87,OP,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k510}It's time to take a top
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:14.40,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k700}徘徊於惡魔之路  並活著走出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.84,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k244}這邂逅是命數嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:22.90,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k606}覺醒之地便是真實的夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:37.30,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k329}在比神話更久遠的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:40.75,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k309}我是火焰之鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.78,0:22:47.52,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k674}離開王的肩膀  飛向赤紅的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.37,0:22:51.51,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k314}何等漫長的旅途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.84,0:22:54.76,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k292}記憶中與沙石共舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:57.87,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k287}此刻撲向你的懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.08,0:23:01.74,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k366}即使終於平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:06.89,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k505}依然要把雙翼化作長劍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:14.60,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k676}就讓愛穿越戰場墮落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:19.16,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k417}身穿緋紅的荊棘之戰鎧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.91,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k375}若這具肉體要化作死花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.91,0:23:31.61,ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be1}{\k870}我願意在你的劍下華麗的綻放
